message.text:
🚨𝐒𝐞𝐞𝐤𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝟐 𝐔𝐍𝐈𝐓𝐒 𝐎𝐅 𝐓𝐘𝐏𝐄 𝐎+ 𝐁𝐥𝐨𝐨𝐝 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐮𝐬𝐢𝐨𝐧🚨

We are in immediate need of blood donors of 𝐎+ 𝗕𝗟𝗢𝗢𝗗 𝗧𝗬𝗣𝗘 for Direct Transfusion. All necessary donor eligibility information is included in the post below. Please read thoroughly and follow the instructions provided.

If you're willing and eligible to donate, kindly send a direct message or contact the person listed. All monetary transactions that may arise are highly encouraged to be settled in person to avoid scam. 

Your support could save a life. Thank you so much for your generosity!🩸❤️

Your support could save a life. Thank you so much for your generosity!🩸❤️
